SM Flying Cat

Flappy Bird
===========

• On effect awake
isPlaying = false;
isGameStarted = false;

• On Game start
isPlaying = true;
isGameStarted = true;

• Lost game; Next tap will reset the game
isPlaying = false;
isGameStarted = true;

Resetting the game
- Reposition player and obstacles to original position
- Reset

• After game reset
isPlaying = false;
isGameStarted = false;


